definition:
Someone descended from Elon, a man of the tribe of Zebulun living at the time of Egypt and Wilderness, first mentioned at Gen.46.14; 
 son of: Zebulun (H2074); 
 brother of: Sered (H5624) and Jahleel (H3177)
Group of e.lon (אֵלוֹן "Elon" H0356H) 
 § Elonite = "might" or "terebinth: a plain"
 one of the clan of Elon
